review_blob: At first: love the bottle, very nice design. Than the smell.. the first I had did actually smell like weed, which is a weird but not unpleasant experience. The taste is flavoured by its smell I guess. I like it. Its special, Im just not sure yet if thats 100% positive...
Very full taste, and youll definetely feel the alcohol. Drink with patience. Try to really taste it.
A stronger version of the standard Hertog Jan. Good!
The best pilsener. Get it when you can.
Lovely, high alcohol percentage and you taste its strongness all the way.. Excellent beer!
Strong and tastefull bock beer. Very good!
A bit disappointing.. could have been better, but it tasted like a weak bock beer... Not too bad, but actually a big disappointment.
I had this one on an alcohol-free-party.. probably a bad bottle, but it had a sweet taste like lemonade...
Nice, not too special, but a good taste.
Maybe if Im thirsty or something...
